OL,6,FThe opening of a new cancer centre in
OL,7,Fhas been delayed until 2027.
OL,9,FIt was initially hoped that would open
OL,10,Fin the city in 2024, however, it has
OL,11,Fnow been pushed back three years.
OL,13,FThe current Velindre Cancer Centre is
OL,14,Fmore than 68 years old and serves the
OL,15,F1.7 million patient population of
OL,16,Fsoutheast Wales and others further
OL,17,Fafield.
