OL,6,FIt delivers a range of non-surgical
OL,7,Ftertiary cancer services for the
OL,8,Fregion in partnership with Aneurin
OL,9,FBevan, Cardiff and Vale and Cwm Taf
OL,10,FMorgannwg University Health Boards and
OL,11,FPowys Teaching Health Board.
OL,13,FOver the years since plans were
OL,14,Fapproved, campaigners have voiced
OL,15,Ftheir concerns over how the
OL,16,Fconstruction of the new centre will
OL,17,Faffect the Northern Meadows in the
OL,18,FWhitchurch area of the city.
