OL,6,FCampaigners have staged several
OL,7,Fprotests in recent years, with as
OL,8,Fworkers began clearing vegetation on
OL,9,Fthe site.
OL,11,FProtesters occupied the land as work
OL,12,Fbegan at the site as they believe it
OL,13,Frepresents some of Cardiff's last
OL,14,Fremaining green meadows and ancient
OL,15,Fwoodland.
OL,17,FThe new centre promises to deliver "a
OL,18,Fvital world-class facility" and was
OL,19,Fexpected to open its doors to its
OL,20,Ffirst patients this year.
