OL,6,FHowever, the Velindre Trust has
OL,7,Fconfirmed that the opening is now
OL,8,Fscheduled for 2027.
OL,10,FThe trust said it had reached a
OL,11,F"significant milestone" in reaching an
OL,12,Fagreement with the Acorn consortium to
OL,13,Fdesign, build and maintain the new
OL,14,Fcentre.
