OL,4,Cuntil 2027
OL,6,FVelindre University NHS Trust Chief
OL,7,FExecutive Steve Ham said: "This marks
OL,8,Fa major milestone in the project to
OL,9,Fbuild our much-needed new cancer
OL,10,Fcentre. We are proud of the work our
OL,11,Fstaff do day in, day out to treat,
OL,12,Fcare and support patients from all
OL,13,Fover southeast Wales.
OL,15,F"Now, we will build a world-class NHS
OL,16,Ffacility that will support our staff
OL,17,Fto deliver care of the highest
OL,18,Fstandard for cancer patients across
OL,19,Fsoutheast Wales and beyond.
