OL,6,F"It will be an inspiring workplace for
OL,7,Four dedicated staff to thrive and
OL,8,Fsupport internationally renowned
OL,9,Fcancer research and collaboration
OL,10,Facross the region. The new centre will
OL,11,Fbe a long-lasting feature of the wider
OL,12,FNHS Wales estate and create a
OL,13,Fbenchmark for environmental
OL,14,Fsustainability."
OL,16,FProject Director David Powell added:
OL,17,F"I want to thank all our incredibly
OL,18,Fdedicated staff for their
OL,19,Fcontributions in getting us to this
OL,20,Fpivotal milestone.
